Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.03,0:00:05.01,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,In 1940, the Tacoma\NNarrows Bridge looked
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.01,0:00:06.98,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,like the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:10.51,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,It was long, slender,\Ncheaper than the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.51,0:00:13.16,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,original conservative\Ndesign, and beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.16,0:00:15.80,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,enough to make its\Nmovement famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.73,0:00:19.55,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,People called it\NGalloping Gertie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.34,0:00:21.61,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,But the wind on collapse\Nday was
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.61,0:00:22.87,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,not extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.67,0:00:24.93,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The bridge had already\Nsurvived stronger autumn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.93,0:00:26.18,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:28.22,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The hidden problem was\Nwhat the bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:29.40,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,did to the air after it\Nstarted
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.40,0:00:30.57,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.54,0:00:33.72,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Its shallow solid plate\Ngirder deck was
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:35.91,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,too flexible in torsion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:38.37,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Once the roadway began\Nto twist, the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.37,0:00:40.85,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,motion changed the\Nairflow, and the changed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:43.33,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,airflow fed the next\Ntwist.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.33,0:00:46.13,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Engineers were studying\Nthe motion, but the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.13,0:00:47.94,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,design culture had not\Nyet made dynamic
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:49.74,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,aerodynamic testing\Nroutine for bridges like
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.74,0:00:51.55,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:54.17,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The bridge did not just\Nmeet wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.04,0:00:56.27,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,It entered a behavior\Nits own design
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.27,0:00:57.50,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,made possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.52,0:01:01.79,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Small causes, massive\Nconsequences.
